<h1 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 22px; color: #111111;">Application accepted</h1>
<p style="color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Hi <%= @first_name %>,
</p>
<p style="color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Great news - your maker application has been accepted.
</p>
<p style="color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Please schedule your live verification session here:
</p>
<p style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @scheduling_link %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #D4F93D; color: #111111; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 999px;">
    Schedule verification
  </a>
</p>
<p style="color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  If the button does not work, use this link:<br>
  <a href="<%= @scheduling_link %>" style="color: #0A5BD8;"><%= @scheduling_link %></a>
</p>
